      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice utente                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      s-ute                to   r-env-cod-ute          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Date and time da segreteria             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DT"                 to   s-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
